summary: Meet Anaré Indoril. She\'s a Dunmer Thief with exquisite skills with a bow and an arrow.
descriptionHtml:
Meet Anaré Indoril. She\'s a Dunmer Thief with exquisite skills with a bow and an arrow. She wears a Grey Thief Armor which is based on Linwe\'s Armor. I inspired from Karliah while creating her. She resides at the Silver-Blood Inn in Markarth, leaning to a wall.

INFO:
Works perfectly with UFO as long as UFO loads after this mod.
Works with No More Blocky Faces.

REQUIREMENTS:
Better Females by Bella
Probably the latest Update

UPDATES COMING:
I\'m planning to add a storyline and a mini-quest for her. But i need some scripters first, If you are good at scripting and coding, you can PM me.

USAGE OF MOD:
You can use this mod in your own mod with my permission, You can upload it to other sites by giving me credit. If you\'re going to give me a \'lil credit, I think there won\'t be any problem.

SPECIAL THANKS TO:
Bethesda.
Griffin178 (For testing the UFO compability)
author: Birusk
